data.text:
2023-24 Topps UEFA Club Competitions (CHECKLIST ADDED AT THE BOTTOM!)

The UEFA Hobby Season is back with a bang with the new and improved Topps UEFA Club Competitions 2023/24, now releasing earlier than ever before!

The collection promises to set new standards, each box now guarantees 1 Autograph or Relic card! The biggest stars and rookies of the UEFA Club Competitions are included, as well as legends of the past, like Ronaldinho, Zinédine Zidane and Wayne Rooney!

There is a 200-card base set. Besides, it showcases the 3 Title Winners from last years' UEFA Club Competitions, 5 unique Combo Cards, and a total of 15 Future Stars.

There are more new cards to chase! New inserts like EUROPEAN NIGHTS, BEST OF THE BEST: 2022/23 MOMENTS and HISTORIC HAT-TRICKS! Of course, the inserts we have seen before are also included once again, like the ROAD TO THE FINAL and NOW STARRING. Special CHROME MOJO cards can be found in each case on top of that!

As always, the highlights of the collection are the desirable Relic and Autograph cards, which bring you closer to the stars. Can you find autos from legends such as Paul Gascoigne and Luis Figo, or from Real Madrid’s blockbuster transfer Jude Bellingham? Look out for rare on-card autographs in lucky boxes!

BASE CARDS

Look out for Base Card Short Prints, Super Short Prints and Ultra Short Prints!

BASE PARALLEL CARDS

• Pink Sparkle Parallel - 3 Per Hobby Box.

• Purple FB Parallel - sequentially #’d to 299.

• Navy Blue Parallel - sequentially #’d to 250.

• Neon Green Parallel - sequentially numbered to 199.

• Black & White Icy Parallel - sequentially numbered to 150.

• Blue Inferno Parallel - sequentially numbered to 125. HOBBY EXCLUSIVE

• Green FB Parallel - sequentially #’d to 99.

• Icy Blue FB Parallel - sequentially #’d to 75.

• Red FB Parallel - sequentially #’d to 5.

• Base Card Super Short Prints - The 10 most collectable Topps players.

• Base Card Ultra Short Prints - Honoring Cristiano Ronaldo.
